The ''Ruckus Wireless'' logo and "GD 11" is silkscreened on the board in the FCC photos. :"FAB 100-11133-001 REV 3" is on the other side of the board.
Per the FCC manual, the default SSID format is ''WirelessX'' (where ''X'' is a number). :Default credentials are per the FCC label.
Likely [[Atheros]] AR7161+AR9220+AR9223/AR9227 device.. {{See also|Ruckus Wireless ZoneFlex 7351}}
